data.meta_description: The 2023 NBA Draft saw the Portland Trail Blazers add three new players, including third-overall pick Scoot Henderson. Fans are unsurprisingly hyped about this team's future and ready to see this class in action
data.text:
The 2023 NBA Draft saw the Portland Trail Blazers add three new players, including third-overall pick Scoot Henderson. Fans are unsurprisingly hyped about this team's future and ready to see this class in action.

The good news for the Blazers faithful is that Portland will be showcasing its future in Las Vegas, Nevada in just a few weeks. With that in mind, here's everything you need to know about the Trail Blazers' 2023 Summer League schedule, roster, and results.

Trail Blazers Summer League Roster 2023

The Trail Blazers' 2023 Summer League roster is headlined by No. 3 overall pick Scoot Henderson and No. 23 Kris Murray. A number of NBA veterans and undrafted players will join them as the team participates in the Las Vegas tournament

Trail Blazers Summer League Schedule and Results 2023

The Trail Blazers will be appearing at the main NBA Summer League tournament in Las Vegas from July 7-17, where they'll play a minimum of five games.
